-- China’s Hu Calls, Congratulates North Korea’s Kim Jong Un on Appointment
-- B y   L i z a   L i n
-- 2012-01-02T00:12:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-02/china-s-hu-calls-congratulates-north-korea-s-kim-jong-un-on-appointment.html
China ’s President  Hu Jintao 
congratulated Kim Jong Un on his appointment as  North Korea ’s
“supreme commander” in a phone call on Dec. 31, according to a
government statement.  China has enjoyed a “traditionally strong friendship”
with its North Korean neighbor in the past and will maintain and
strengthen those relations in the coming year, Hu said,
according to a statement posted on the foreign ministry’s
website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
